@PORT = 3002

### Get all news (with optional filters)
GET http://localhost:{{PORT}}/api/news?page=1&limit=10&catagory=Technology&keyword=Sample
Accept: application/json

### Create a news item
POST http://localhost:{{PORT}}/api/news/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sample News Title",
  "description": "Short description of the news.",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",
  "content": "Full content of the news article.",
  "category": "Technology"
}

### Get all categories
GET http://localhost:{{PORT}}/api/catagories
Accept: application/json
